c: 3
v: 110
t: "Ndimi (maMuslim) boka revanhu rakanaka rakapuhwa vanhu, munokomekedza kuita mabasa akanaka uye nekurambidza kuita mabasa akaipa, uye munotenda muna Allah. Uye dai vanhu vakapihwa Gwaro (maJudha nemaKristu) vakatenda, zvirokwazvo zvingadai zvakavanakira; pakati pavo pane vamwe vanotenda, asi vazhinji vavo vanoita mabasa akaipa"